\prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(1-\frac{1}{2k}\right)/ \prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(1-\frac{1}{2k+1}\right) = \prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(\frac{1-\frac{1}{2k}}{1-\frac{1}{2k+1}}\right) = \prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(1-\frac{1}{4k^2}\right)
\prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(a_{k}\right)/ \prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(b_{k}\right) = \prod_{k=1}^{n} \left(\frac{a_{k}}{b_{k}}\right) 
n
\frac{\prod_{k=1}^{n} (1-\frac{1}{2k})}{\prod_{k=1}^{n}(1 - \frac{1}{2k+1})} = \frac{(1-\frac{1}{2})(1-\frac{1}{4}) \times \ldots \times (1-\frac{1}{2n})}{(1-\frac{1}{3})(1-\frac{1}{5}) \times \ldots \times (1-\frac{1}{2n+1})}
